column6: Who is Stephen Strange? Months ago, in a chance encounter, he saved a woman's life--and since then, she's devoted every waking moment to tracking him down and learning his secrets! But her investigations are taking her down a very dangerous road of magic and mysticism--and straight towards one of Strange's oldest foes! Rated T  ...$3.99
column8: | penciller:Tomm Coker | colorist:Daniel Freedman | colorist:Christina Strain | inker:Emma Rios | writer:Mark Waid
